attributes.name: ObserverSet
attributes.description:
ObserverSet is a data structure used to keep track of observers that have been deferred.

It ensures that observers are called in the same order that they were initially triggered.

It also ensures that observers for any object-key pairs are called only once, even if they were triggered multiple times while deferred. In this case, the order that the observer is called in will depend on the first time the observer was triggered.
